name: Pendulumucho
desc:
Pendulum Effect
Once per turn, during your Main Phase, if this card was activated this turn: You can target 1 of your Pendulum Monsters, that is banished or in your Graveyard, except "Pendulumucho"; add it to your Extra Deck face-up.

Monster Effect
If this card is Normal or Special Summoned: You can Special Summon 1 face-up Level 1 Pendulum Monster from your Extra Deck, except "Pendulumucho", but banish it when it leaves the field.
